{"sn45.21:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 45.21 ","sn45.21:0.2":"3. Micchattavagga ","sn45.21:0.3":"Micchattasutta ","sn45.21:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn45.21:1.2":"“Micchattanca vo, bhikkhave, desessami, sammattanca. ","sn45.21:1.3":"Tam sunatha. ","sn45.21:1.4":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, micchattam? ","sn45.21:1.5":"Seyyathidam—micchaditthi …pe… micchasamadhi. ","sn45.21:1.6":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, micchattam. ","sn45.21:1.7":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, sammattam? ","sn45.21:1.8":"Seyyathidam—sammaditthi …pe… sammasamadhi. ","sn45.21:1.9":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, sammattan”ti. ","sn45.21:1.10":"Pathamam. "}